(Corrects time of release for Labor Force Survey in first
paragraph.)  Statistics South Africa  releases its
fourth-quarter Labor Force Survey at 11:30 a.m. in  Pretoria .    South Africa , which has the highest unemployment rate of 62
countries tracked by Bloomberg, added fewer jobs in the third
quarter than the previous three months with employment in
formal, non-agricultural industries rising 0.2 percent, or
17,000, to 8.15 million.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vernon Wessels in Johannesburg at 
